task.summary: Added a setup resources bash script to create the models needed for the app
User's can now be added from the active admin interface
Added a workout page to active admin
Added paperclip gem to enable image uploads. Exercises were reconfigured to include images using paperclip. Active Admin console now allow the user to add images to exercises.
Made public static files available in production environment.
Changed the location that exercise images are uploaded to.
Made changes to seed file after changing the way images are saved
Fixed an error after changing image source. Json now displays from index.
